Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.34,0:00:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I can't do it." "It's too frustrating."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.97,0:00:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Break down those hurdles.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.14,0:00:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is nothing I can't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.31,0:00:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who is being manipulated on the field?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.82,0:00:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not frightened yet I get told to go away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The path to the unseen future...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.87,0:00:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I may not be able to choose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.42,0:00:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Close your eyes, and shuffle your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.51,0:00:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Definitely, just like cards
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.26,0:01:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As promised, yes! you are the winner
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Never lose! Shuffle your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.10,0:01:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}definitely, just like cards
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.73,0:01:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ever since that miracle...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.42,0:01:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H36A637&}Ectoplasmer{\r}, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.03,0:01:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Magician's Disciple:\NBlack Magician Girl"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.27,0:01:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r}, I won't let you sacrifice your soul for me in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:02:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I sacrificed my {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r} in order to finish off Yugi, but...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.50,0:02:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was all in vain...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.83,0:02:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait just a little longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, he's lost his {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r} as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.51,0:02:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In my deck I still have two more {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r}s waiting to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.17,0:02:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Continue the duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.43,0:02:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My End Phase!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card set!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.53,0:02:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, I know. You don't have another Black Magician in your deck, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.00,0:02:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The true title of the {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r} user goes to me after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.34,0:02:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see about that, Pandora.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.72,0:02:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you truly are the true {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r} user, you should have heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mourn of the card's soul who was betrayed by his master!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.26,0:03:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't hear anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only sound filling my ears...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the buzz of the circular saw about to cut you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.48,0:03:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, you only have 700 points of your Life left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the moment it hits 0, the cutter will slice into you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I will conduct the perfect ending to the greatest escape show!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.86,0:03:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cards decide how the fight ends!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go! My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.02,0:03:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now, Pandora has no monsters on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This may be my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon {\c&H3896AE&}Gazelle the King of Mythical Beasts{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fell right into my trap, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.45,0:03:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Card! {\c&H911ADE&}Demon's Scale{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.11,0:03:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Trap Card is activated when the opponent Summons a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging by the number of monsters I have on the field, it will make your field equal to that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.97,0:04:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...! The number of monsters he has on the field is 0! That means...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.89,0:04:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.22,0:04:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H911ADE&}Demon's Scale{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.72,0:04:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My monsters are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the number on both our fields is 0!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shame, since you just Summoned a new monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.46,0:04:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.99,0:04:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this card, my victory is guaranteed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Both of our fields have no monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That means he shouldn't be able to sacrifice lower level monsters
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:04:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to Summon a more powerful one...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.81,0:05:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, it seems you think you've read through my strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the contrary, I have a card that will let me Summon a high level monster in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A card that will let me call the best magician, {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An Instant Summon card...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going! This is the key card to victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H36A637&}Black Magic Curtain{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This turn, the player will pay half his Life Points as a cost
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to Summon the black magician from their deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth! {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:06:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, how do you like my perfect Magician Deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.37,0:06:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon speed, quick acting, and magic combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Including everything, it surpasses your deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.02,0:06:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one worthy of being called the true {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r} user, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.41,0:06:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, you have no monster guarding you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This turn, If I were to attack you with {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's certain that your Life would diminish and that I would win.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing guarding you is that set card on your field.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.32,0:06:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely, it is a Trap Card that activates when an attack is launched,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it wipes out the attacking monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an eyesore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.26,0:06:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't I seal that set card?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seal my set card?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card, {\c&H36A637&}Magic-Sealing Arrows{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now all of your remaining hope has been sealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r}, attack the player directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.56,0:07:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H36A637&}Black Magic Curtain{\r} is... on Yugi's field?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The Magic Card you played, {\c&H36A637&}Black Magic Curtain{\r}, is a card that affects the entire field.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, I am also allowed to use that magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will also Summon a Magician Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.21,0:07:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...! You shouldn't have another {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r} in your deck...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.99,0:07:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I have only one {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r} in my deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.37,0:07:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-T-Then what are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the world of Duel Monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is but one female magician that is called the "Magician's Disciple".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.40,0:08:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...! There is a Magician Card that I, the Magicians user, don't know about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.78,0:08:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2040A9&}Black Magician Girl{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2040A9&}B{\r}-{\c&H2040A9&}Black Magician Girl{\r}...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.68,0:08:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But {\c&H2040A9&}Black Magician Girl{\r}'s Attack is only 2000!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can do nothing against {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r}'s attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r}, attack {\c&H2040A9&}Black Magician Girl{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.88,0:08:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magic!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.26,0:08:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Burning!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...! My {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r} is disappearing...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.18,0:09:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Attack should be 500 higher...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you. {\c&H2040A9&}Black Magician Girl{\r}, for each {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r} sleeping in the Graveyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,increases her Attack by 300 points for each.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The soul of a fallen ally makes her stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.78,0:09:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.18,0:09:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r} in Yugi's Graveyard...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.15,0:09:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with an increase of 300 points, her Attack should still only be 2300!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.65,0:09:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r} should still have won!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look closer. If you are truly a {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r} user, the truth should spread out before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:09:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-There's one more...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.68,0:10:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way...! My {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r}'s soul... is there as well!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2040A9&}Black Magician Girl{\r} inherits the souls of {\i1}all{\i0} {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r}s sleeping in our Graveyards!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.66,0:10:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Betrayed by you, your {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r}'s soul has chosen to fight against you instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourself, Pandora!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2040A9&}Black Magician Girl{\r}, direct attack player Pandora!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.69,0:11:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Burning!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you betrayed your cards, you've lost, Pandora!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi guys, What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda, Yugi's gone missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely, he's been captured by the Ghouls!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother lead us to this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you know the location, then it's a different story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.20,0:11:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's break in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.22,0:11:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a duelist, to not cherish the bond between your cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're only walking down the path of failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lost because you disrespected your {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible! A duelist who respects their cards...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.27,0:11:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A card should only follow the instructions of the master controlling it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A duelist like you who threw away the bonds between your cards
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to obtain victory...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.79,0:12:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've already lost the duelist's soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pandora, all that awaits you is your last act of cruelty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.40,0:12:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When my counter hits 0, the cutter will be triggered,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's moving to saw through my legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GET AWAY~!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.71,0:12:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The key and Puzzle Card...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it... that sound...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.14,0:12:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.47,0:12:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't dare underestimate a conjurer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought over this possible outcome, and prepared a spare key in my sleeve!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as I have this, I can still escape from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I scared? So scared I can't move?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.98,0:13:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save me! Please let me off the hook, Malik-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh...? The key's gone...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I WAS JUST HOLDING THE KEY A MOMENT AGO...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pandora!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lost the duel. You have to pay the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just altered your memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.00,0:13:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your memory of that key just faded away right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To you, the key may as well not {\i1}exist{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you in there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer us if you're in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.21,0:13:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,LOOK OUT!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's definitely wrong to throw your life away for a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine... Catherine...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CATHERINE~!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CATHERINE~!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't leave my side again...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.02,0:14:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Catherine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry I didn't accept your feelings then and drove you away...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.13,0:14:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about my fame anymore...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's both return to France together and start over...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pandora-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.42,0:14:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you go and do {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.16,0:14:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the vessel for the other Yugi, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.71,0:14:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His personality changed suddenly...! You are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.80,0:14:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You weren't conscious when we met earlier today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Malik.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.64,0:15:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.45,0:15:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can control people from any location. I can even alter their memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I ease off enough, their voices can still be heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I controlled Keith using this same method.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. In order to prove the existence of your other self.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To see if you were really the one chosen to solve the Millennium Puzzle,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.15,0:15:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and to see if the man inside you was who I thought he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.77,0:15:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when you completed the Millennium Puzzle again,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you confirmed the existence of that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you wanna kill us?! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't concern {\i1}you{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have business with the soul you contain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the heir of the clan of Tomb Guardians who lived in darkness for 3,000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I {\i1}will{\i0} avenge them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the edge of Necropolis in Egypt...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We Tomb Guardians have lived apart from the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,hiding in the shadows, passing the task from mother to daughter and father to son.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.67,0:16:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My clan must avoid all contact with the outside world,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,living only to protect the Millennium Items we were handed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must die for this fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must return the Pharaoh's memory to his soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.79,0:16:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge...? Clan of Tomb Keepers?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.58,0:16:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Memory...? Does that mean the Pharaoh's memory stone tablet
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the 7 items are related?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three God Cards...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I hold one of the seven secrets as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must guard it, even if it means my life, until I present it to the Pharaoh's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.79,0:16:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I was taught as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.43,0:17:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is {\i1}finding{\i0} the Pharaoh's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only clue is written in the original Ancient Egyptian hieroglyphic text
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the Pert Em Heru, the Book of the Dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It says of the Pharaoh "You will know him by the three God Cards he wields."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the one who collects the three God Cards will be crowned the title "Pharaoh"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and regain the Millennium Items and his lost memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost memory?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New Pharaoh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.67,0:17:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For countless generations, my clan has protected
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Millennium Items at the cost of suffering and pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Including my {\i1}father{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.56,0:17:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will put an end to the curse laid upon us...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to do that, I will take revenge on the Pharaoh's soul and kill him a {\i1}second{\i0} time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if the prophecy says that the Pharaoh will wield the three God Cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then I will obtain the cards and become the {\i1}new{\i0} Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I formed the Ghouls for the sole purpose of locating those God Cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.19,0:18:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I have already obtained two of the cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.65,0:18:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The third resides in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this Battle City!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.22,0:18:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally understand what it is the other me is looking for in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.05,0:18:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's his lost memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we don't locate the God Cards and the other me's lost memory, I can stay with him forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.68,0:18:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The other me knew this well in his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For his precious memory, he saw our future.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But the other me doesn't know his memories, so he can only stay where he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even so, he continues to search.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If that's the case, there's no point being sad about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:19:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if, when he obtains that memory, we are to be separated...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.82,0:19:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll gladly help him search!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.47,0:19:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik! I won't let you take away the other me's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're merely a vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the time comes, you can die {\i1}alongside{\i0} him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Within this city, another Rare Hunter wielding a God Card is lurking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.62,0:19:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man who holds {\c&H0000F5&}Osiris the Heaven Dragon{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.40,0:19:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H0000F5&}Osiris the Heaven Dragon{\r}...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.67,0:19:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He will appear before you sooner than you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So remember... beware the Silent Doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silent Doll...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall obtain the three God Cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Yugi, once I kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.68,0:18:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I will be freed from my family's cursed fate, and the world will be mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll meet again, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.40,0:19:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll fight in order to get back his lost memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, Yugi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.06,0:19:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.56,0:20:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just you wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.24,0:20:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alongside your impertinent vessel, I will bury your soul in darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How will you get the God Card?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use a God Card against a God Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, holding the {\c&H25C0E7&}Ra{\r} card, will enter Domino City shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.98,0:20:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're going against Kaiba {\i1}personally{\i0}, Lord Malik?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, it will come to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.78,0:20:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm focusing on Yugi for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the Silent Doll out of his stall and set him loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.20,0:20:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.05,0:20:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt he's going to make things really {\i1}fun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.86,0:20:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fun...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.12,0:20:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lord Malik rarely uses that word unless he's thinking terrible thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gathering together the three God Cards is supposed to be the Ghoul's primary objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.29,0:20:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Lord Malik is focusing on Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.80,0:21:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The {\c&H25C0E7&}Ra{\r} card...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.05,0:21:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, with these hands, I will surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Swearing by the scars on my back, I will {\b0}defeat{\b1} you and get my revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.68,0:21:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dear sister, I can't forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.97,0:21:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The man who killed our clan and our father! Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.96,0:21:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone wants Jounouchi's autograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.47,0:21:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't he just stealing your Duel Disk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.89,0:21:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He manages to get it back, although...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems his rare card was stolen by Insector Haga!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.45,0:21:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Filled with anger, Jounouchi challenges Haga to a duel, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.03,0:21:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:21:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a card like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.69,0:22:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap of Revenge
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.60,0:22:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reckless! Parasite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.44,0:22:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.29,0:22:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel like I've been here, been in this place before
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.72,0:22:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the classroom shaded by the setting sun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.14,0:22:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I laughed along and pointed with my too shortly cut bangs
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.24,0:22:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Little by little, time keeps going
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.54,0:23:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My bangs now over my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.71,0:23:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sunset took everyone together
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.92,0:23:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure nothing changed while we were there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.18,0:23:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.35,0:23:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I kept on searching for something
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.52,0:23:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you understood such a senseless time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.69,0:23:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was the answer
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.41,0:23:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From here, always...
